title: Geometry Dash FreezeNova
description:
Give yourself over to the beat of the song!  Discover the FreezeNova difference while playing the well-known arcade game Geometry Dash.  In Geometry Dash FreezeNova, the challenging arcade game, your goal is to keep the cube clear of every obstacle on the flowing surface. Â 
Like with the original Geometry Dash, playing this game is most enjoyable when you give in to the music's beat.
